{"tid":506052,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"最近又翻睇左一部OVA","createTime":"2017-12-21T21:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T11:31:53.000Z","uid":61889,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b58a8ed9c9875c7cb37e37edac52ae10b54e1e63","tid":506052,"uid":61889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T21:07:33.000Z","msg":"Hellsing Ultimate (厄夜怪客)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/004442_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F004442_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg&h=8329feb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n           世界觀融合吸血鬼 ,宗教 ,納粹主義等元素 ,故事走黑暗暴力血腥路線 ,時間線位於二戰半世紀後,主要圍繞英國王立國教騎士團(Hellsing) ,梵諦岡 ,納粹殘黨三方既衝突 ,引導讀者反思何謂人同何謂怪物。 <br />\n           一共十集,每集片長50分鐘,劇情緊湊無冷場,由於係OVA既關係尺度十分大,除左血肉橫飛既打鬥場面之外,仲有屍姦,殺嬰等敏感情節。每一場戰鬥都預算十足, 流暢既動作配搭每個角色對能力既運用, 打到爆哂血斷哂手腳既場面再加上BGM既襯托, 完全將暴力美學演繹得淋漓盡致。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/020532_f78b898ad27500a72d4a9c7462dd6b5d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F020532_f78b898ad27500a72d4a9c7462dd6b5d.gif&h=3b688661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023645_fa11294ef13c4e63c829ecd631aa8bfe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023645_fa11294ef13c4e63c829ecd631aa8bfe.gif&h=fc2776d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/024522_3f3e8b6b90d57f6ed8db25e0c33099f0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F024522_3f3e8b6b90d57f6ed8db25e0c33099f0.gif&h=8deea1db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n            Hellsing對角色既描寫為整套作品加分不少, 劇中每個角色都有自己既夢想同信念, 尤其阿卡多, 神父, 少校三個貫串全篇故事既人物直到最後都堅守住自己既信念, 佢地唔係好人, 但佢地絕對係有血有肉既真男人, 簡單介紹下。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>阿卡多 </ins><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/031642_2fa240c658c04d0a05d08d3a20c29bc4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F031642_2fa240c658c04d0a05d08d3a20c29bc4.gif&h=1ad04b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/033623_66e7322e756672b532264488b268e85c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F033623_66e7322e756672b532264488b268e85c.gif&h=be58ea43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n           本作主角, 最強吸血鬼, 隸屬Hellsing組織, 專門獵殺其他吸血鬼, 由第一集屈到最後一集, 能夠透過吸取死人既血將其轉化為自己生命, 曾經吸取過300萬死人既血, 實際上同不死身無分別, 除神父外幾乎無人可以令佢認真打, 認為自己只係一隻弱小既怪物, 一直希望被人類殺死, 以了結自己可悲既生命。故事最後中左少校陰招, 成功擺脫吸血鬼既身份。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>神父</ins><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/035515_3150a2a62551d5cd08d9d4e97180afd0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F035515_3150a2a62551d5cd08d9d4e97180afd0.gif&h=f1f83119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/035600_58d888ce694b9da7a323406386525ce8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F035600_58d888ce694b9da7a323406386525ce8.gif&h=31d6596c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/035717_95731174ca915ba930b7b902a2bf6393.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F035717_95731174ca915ba930b7b902a2bf6393.gif&h=943d6e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/040427_97f195b5d5cc6319295ff83170024141.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F040427_97f195b5d5cc6319295ff83170024141.gif&h=a9f0596b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n             隸屬梵諦岡, 敵視天主教外所有宗教, 為守衛天主教不惜違背教義殺死異教徒, 極度鄙視有違神論既吸血鬼。<br />\n             自身經過科學改造, 具有一定既身體復原能力, 可以將聖經化為統劍, 聖經又可以用黎防禦同傳送, 每次打架都會有一堆聖經係身邊飄黎飄去。<br />\n             最後為左打低主角不惜犧牲自己, 同時係主角最尊敬既人。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>少校</ins><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/042726_fda14d22f0d7b49093c594487e0e97d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F042726_fda14d22f0d7b49093c594487e0e97d3.jpg&h=e57d7705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n           納粹殘黨首領, 戰爭狂人, 毫無戰鬥力既肥仔, 對自己作為人類既身份十分自豪, 所以希望透過戰爭打敗作為吸血鬼既阿卡多, 率領吸血鬼同狼人軍隊攻打倫敦, 最後經過一連串計謀成功打低吸血鬼身份既阿卡多, 成為故事大贏家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/045149_2c34ad4ee8b4f3dd427a76462511bb0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F045149_2c34ad4ee8b4f3dd427a76462511bb0c.jpg&h=37f80e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n          本作最具人格魅力既角色, 毫無戰鬥力既少校係充滿怪物, 人人戰鬥力都爆燈既世界入面更顯特出, 每次出場總會演講一輪, 為左證明人類內心既強大, 佢連自己條命都可以唔要, 花費半生只求打敗主角, 雖然明知佢視人命如垃圾, 但不知不覺都會比少校既意志吸引到。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/045809_0302674ef37e579d445ee72b7d2c8043.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F045809_0302674ef37e579d445ee72b7d2c8043.gif&h=966b02c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n       有時間既巴打不妨睇下呢部作品, 絕對唔會覺得浪費緊自己時間。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646bbecfb109a9d9356127f0c612cf23a3219632","tid":506052,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T00:24:54.000Z","msg":"有冇link或seed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec92689ca93a8d0c50322876f541f4964cdb5ef","tid":506052,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T00:31:27.000Z","msg":"Amen!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6286b4b25e59dea2f92cb8e2d4d373a3302ed7e","tid":506052,"uid":33888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T03:26:51.000Z","msg":"A叔應該就冇認為自己弱小,不過佢一直都好想死就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外應該介紹埋女主嘛,女主覺醒個到又係好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f3399c2c02c934a04324f9127c8296fa7e37e0","tid":506052,"uid":157304,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T04:11:20.000Z","msg":"屌你介紹到一半劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻唔想睇"},{"pid":"d2f3b48d5cbe39dc31e9c11ac8769b4dda3d5c68","tid":506052,"uid":37890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T04:20:08.000Z","msg":"介紹定劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔撚洗睇啦"},{"pid":"ce8fe608f47582ea17a829fdf0d94ff6f333fe6f","tid":506052,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T04:28:08.000Z","msg":"呢套野好撚好睇，另一套叫飄流武士都好睇"},{"pid":"08aa076594e9ba6baba2ab1546cec190a77e8a15","tid":506052,"uid":56223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T05:23:53.000Z","msg":"好彩睇左幾句就stop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf32b5e0346394563834fece0795151699d29ca","tid":506052,"uid":61889,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T05:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>介紹定劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔撚洗睇啦</blockquote><br />\n我已經避重就輕, 最緊要係貫徹理念同追求夢想過程點樣引去每個角色既下場, 睇過就知角色既下場同生或死根本唔係呢套野既重點, 我就認為講埋都唔會影響到你去欣賞呢部作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf9b3bfcef7b6b550a8149ee1d3929aec47ddbc","tid":506052,"uid":61889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T05:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A叔應該就冇認為自己弱小,不過佢一直都好想死就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外應該介紹埋女主嘛,女主覺醒個到又係好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n弱小指心靈個方面, A叔雖然面對怪物好囂, 但一係強大既人類面前就180度轉變, 佢自己當時怕死所以選擇左做吸血鬼, 睇得出佢好尊敬堅持保持人類身份既女王, 大小姐, 老管家同神父。<br />\n女主一時賣萌一時又咁型, 唔知由邊方面介紹好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/134740_e1ec47bbc970d6ca9e10331d8d13757a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F134740_e1ec47bbc970d6ca9e10331d8d13757a.jpg&h=ca09f65e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d32c6145cfc5087a7335b69b032a5803b32992d","tid":506052,"uid":61889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T05:53:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢套野好撚好睇，另一套叫飄流武士都好睇</blockquote><br />\n漂流武士淨係睇過原作漫畫, 動畫質素有無Hellsing咁高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5c976a604e22c6bdfd82179b380249524d50f4","tid":506052,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T06:05:25.000Z","msg":"呢套真係成日都有人提, 不過我今日先知原來個紅帽係咁既樣? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係因為唔鍾意紅帽+圓形眼鏡所以唔睇呢套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知原來咁靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbc3358bf92abdd4c06597d0cc482e65f1b964a","tid":506052,"uid":61889,"